Original: Look, Margherita! This city's biggest
draw used to be its view of Yggdrasil,
but see how it's changed...
Translation: Look, Margherita! This city's biggest
draw used to be its view of Yggdrasil,
but see how it's changed...

Original: New explorers still come through the
city gates... I look forward to
meeting these enterprising youths!
Translation: New explorers still come through the
city gates... I look forward to
meeting these enterprising youths!

Original: Welcome to Tharsis! Haven't seen you
around, I don't think. Are you guys
explorers too?
Translation: Welcome to Tharsis! Haven't seen you
around, I don't think. Are you guys
explorers too?

Original: A lovely square, don't you think?
Travellers pass through it, carrying
their dreams in their hearts.
Translation: A lovely square, don't you think?
Travellers pass through it, carrying
their dreams in their hearts.

Original: Tharsis is filled with many races and
ancient knowledge, and this place is
its heart. I hope you like it here.
Translation: Tharsis is filled with many races and
ancient knowledge, and this place is
its heart. I hope you like it here.

Original: Ah... so you heard the rumors of the
[Guild] Guild and came here. Haha,
you're far from the only ones...
Translation: Ah... so you heard the rumors of the
[Guild] Guild and came here. Haha,
you're far from the only ones...

Original: Heya! Welcome ta da ＃1 shop for
explorers! We gots bushi katanas, we
gots drive blades... We got it all!
Translation: Heya! Welcome ta da ＃1 shop for
explorers! We gots bushi katanas, we
gots drive blades... We got it all!

Original: Have you never seen a Vessel or
Sentinel before? Our city is unique
in that it is home to many races.
Translation: Have you never seen a Vessel or
Sentinel before? Our city is unique
in that it is home to many races.

Original: I was just telling a new Imperial how
[Guild] defeated the [Enemy1:175].
Would you like to listen in?
Translation: I was just telling a new Imperial how
[Guild] defeated the [Enemy1:175].
Would you like to listen in?

Original: You seem to be explorers. If you want
to see the Medium, use a Geomagnetic
Pole or a skyship.
Translation: You seem to be explorers. If you want
to see the Medium, use a Geomagnetic
Pole or a skyship.

Original: I suppose I could guide you... Oh?
You'd rather try and manage on your
own? The mark of a great explorer...
Translation: I suppose I could guide you... Oh?
You'd rather try and manage on your
own? The mark of a great explorer...

Original: Yeh want a skyship? Sorry, but I
don't dole them out like candy to
yeh rookies.
Translation: Yeh want a skyship? Sorry, but I
don't dole them out like candy to
yeh rookies.

Original: Even the [Guild] Guild did their
time in the Old Forest Mine. Yeh
gotta follow procedure, yeh know?
Translation: Even the [Guild] Guild did their
time in the Old Forest Mine. Yeh
gotta follow procedure, yeh know?

Original: I heard you'll be setting out for the
first time tomorrow. I'll have a fine
dinner waiting for you! Good luck!
Translation: I heard you'll be setting out for the
first time tomorrow. I'll have a fine
dinner waiting for you! Good luck!

Original: Hm? What's the matter, you're lost?
Ah... Then you should take this map.
Translation: Hm? What's the matter, you're lost?
Ah... Then you should take this map.

Original: Don't worry, drawing a map isn't as
hard as you'd think. Pay close
attention. You just start here and...
Translation: Don't worry, drawing a map isn't as
hard as you'd think. Pay close
attention. You just start here and...
